1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
CMD: "fido take a photo every thirty degrees"

2
00:00:04,870 --> 00:00:09,870
CMD: "and then go back to your starting position"

3
00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:43,040
Robot: "I'm not sure what you mean by a photo every 30 degrees.  Should I turn around here 360 degrees?"

4
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:54,240
CMD: "no"

5
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:54,240
CMD: "start where you are and lurk until you are ninety degrees"

6
00:00:56,040 --> 00:01:01,040
CMD: "then turn one eighty degrees"

7
00:00:57,920 --> 00:01:02,920
CMD: "and then do another photo every thirty degrees until you're back to where your current position is"

8
00:01:08,420 --> 00:01:13,420
CMD: "essentially I don't need photos behind you"

9
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:19,050
Robot: "executing..."

10
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:55,400
Robot: "done"

